post_text: Started Ozempic 0.25mg last week. Feeling nauseous especially in the morning. Is this normal?
Anyone else getting headaches with Ozempic? About 2-3 hours after injection.
Been on Ozempic for 3 months. Down 25 lbs, no side effects. Very happy!
Experiencing some dizziness when standing up quickly. Doctor says it is blood sugar related.
Comparing Ozempic and Wegovy. Both work well but Ozempic seems gentler on stomach.
